parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash. The sensor failure can also cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential safety issue.
symptoms: The passenger airbag light stays on
the airbag warning light on the dashboard stays on
the passenger airbag sensor fails to detect an occupant
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
or the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction, leading to potential injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light on the dashboard stays on
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
or the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or catch fire, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power
electrical components malfunctioning
smoke or flames coming from the dashboard or hood
loud clicking sounds
and inability to start the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbag light to illuminate, and the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag light illuminating
airbag sensor malfunctioning
and the airbag not deploying in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Brake lights not functioning
cruise control not disengaging with the brake pedal
and the engine accelerating unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the door lock system can cause the doors to lock or unlock unexpectedly, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Door locks not functioning
doors locking or unlocking unexpectedly
and the door lock buttons not working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the climate control system can cause smoke or flames to come from the air vents, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Smoke or flames coming from the air vents
and the climate control system malfunctioning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Unintended Acceleration (SUA) and Cruise Control Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities. The failure of the cruise control system can also lead to accidents and safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly and uncontrollably
the cruise control system fails to engage or disengage
the vehicle lurches forward
the engine RPMs increase rapidly
and the brakes may be difficult to press.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine revving and surging can cause the vehicle to lurch forward, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents. The sudden surging can also cause wear and tear on the engine, transmission, and brakes.
symptoms: The engine revs suddenly and uncontrollably
the vehicle surges forward
the RPMs increase rapidly
and the brakes may be difficult to press.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Pedal and Anti-Slip Resistance Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal and anti-slip resistance can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. The lack of anti-slip resistance on the pedals can lead to the driver's foot slipping off the brake pedal, causing the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
there is no anti-slip resistance on the pedals
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
and the vehicle accelerates unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and gear shifting can cause the vehicle to lurch forward, making it difficult to control, and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The transmission shifts erratically
the vehicle lurches forward
and the gears do not engage properly.
